Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.69,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,UENAK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:17.70,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TAMBAH LAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.70,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TUANG
