Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mahasiswi Baru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Ketua Asrama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Tidak ada?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibuki menghilang lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua Asrama memang susah\Ndiajak berkelompok, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ya, Mahasiswi Baru.\NSeniormu tidak bisa diteladani.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua Asrama sedang apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti dia "melakukan itu".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak salah lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memanggilnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah, Mahasiswi Baru.\NBiarkan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo makan bekal yang kita bawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin bicara dengan Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin saja dia tersesat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamiina Botan, siap jalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia gadis baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yakin dibiarkan pergi, nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu minum-minum sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, pesan segelas highball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, kamu terlihat sangat muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, kartu identitas, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tidak apa-apa.\NTerima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minum sendirian itu lebih nyaman\Ndan tidak perlu merasa sungkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan begini terus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah menunggu.\NSilakan highball-nya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, lihat itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantik banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke sana, yuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di bawah ada hamparan shibazakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di depan ada Gunung Buko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, bisa-bisanya aku\Nmengabaikan kedua hal itu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan lebih memilih kedai minuman\Nuntuk difoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh amat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampak nikmat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu ragu membiarkannya pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena Ibuki\Nsedang minum-minum, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak suka dilihat orang\Nsaat minum miras.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu cegukan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua Asrama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tungg—\NMahasiswi baru, Kamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf, setiap kali minum—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kamu cegukan saat minum miras, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak minum di depan orang\Nkarena ini memalukan dan tidak sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku suka minuman keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin minum itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak boleh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi kepingin\Nkarena kamu tampak menikmatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu sudah boleh minum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Secara hukum, aku boleh minum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menunda masuk universitas,\Njadi usiaku sudah 20 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kuat minum atau tidak, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya, aku belum pernah\Nmencoba minuman keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku tampak begitu menikmatinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak keberatan dengan highball\Nyang sudah kuminum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu ciuman tidak langsung, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah mabuk, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Nyas-nyus" begitu dan aku tidak tahu—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lemah sama minuman bersoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita berdua sama, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibawa santai saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua juga bisa cegukan atau sendawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Junior baru ini pengertian sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, kamu benar... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu curang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mau berbagi kenikmatan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu imut juga, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tadi bukan kepingin minum,\Ntapi kepingin kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?\NKamu mabuk, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ndak tahu, lah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balik aja, yuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu minum-minum sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku merasa bisa membuka hati\Nuntuk minum bersamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyebabnya pasti...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa teman-teman marah?\N- Karena dia, Kamiina Botan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Katanya, kamu sering begini\N- tampak begitu menikmati miras.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan susah diajak berkelompok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak aja kalau ngomong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baru pulang juga, ya, Kamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok "kerja bagus?"\NIni saja masih siang, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu salam khas para mahasiswa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, selamat siang,\Nselamat malam, selamat tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua itu bisa diganti "kerja bagus".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Selamat pagi" juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dengar itu sebelum beraktivitas,\Nefeknya malah bikin capek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius amat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita minum teh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya kudapan enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mengajakku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang siapa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh saja, tapi aku enggak asyik, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalah asyik atau tidak,\Nakulah yang berhak menilainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau beres-beres dulu,\Njadi tunggulah di luar sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pura-pura, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, ih!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma sebentar, kok!\NJangan mengintip, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Janji, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, deh, iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:11:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, aku akan bawa itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Botol plastiknya sudah beres.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaiannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.\NAku timbun di lemari dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak bakal sempat\Nbuat menyedot debu, nih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang,\Naku akan rajin melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata rumahku tidak bersih sendiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ibuku selalu membersihkannya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf menunggu lama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bawa apaan, tuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, ketahuan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau coba?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:12:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cukup ringan untuk pemula\Ndan tidak mengandung soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kan mengajakmu minum teh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak boleh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak perlu memelas segala\Nsupaya kuizinkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu ingin minum-minum, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cari kata lain, kek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kamu terbiasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, sudah lama aku tidak bersulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamarmu imut banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lihat sana-sini!\NAku jadi malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak banget!\NKukira wine itu agak berat diminum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung aku memilih rasa simpel\Ndan tidak kompleks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya...\NEh, aku harus bilang apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya enak dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga enggak bisa cari kata lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sudah minum berbagai jenis,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu akan tahu aroma dan rasanya
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sehingga bisa berkomentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ada perbedaan\Npersepsi rasa di antara kita, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tu-Tunggu! Kamu dekat banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu curang banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin merasakan wine\Ndengan persepsi rasamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pengin lidahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku punya lidahmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku pasti lebih bisa menikmati wine ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamiina, kamu berubah drastis\Nsetelah minum miras, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, silakan dicicipi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan manju jumangoku\Nsambil minum wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamiina Botan bisa jadi aneh\Nsetelah minum miras.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau mungkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Enaknya.\N- apa semua orang memang begini
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Enak banget.\N- dan hanya aku yang tidak tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Manju-ku, seleraku...\N- Saat minum bersama seseorang,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- aku mengetahui banyak hal baru.\N- Eh? Kamu ngomong apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Kamu enggak tahu iklan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, aku balik dulu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada orang bicara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku minta dibantu mengerjakan tugas!\N- Jam sebegini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Siapa, ya?\N- Kerjakanlah sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hei, lepaskan aku.\N- Ayolah, Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ibuki dan...\N- Ayolah, Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan tinggalkan juniormu ini, Ketua!\N- Kamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Udah, ya, semangat.\N- Aku mohon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak selesai-selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya aku tidak menyerah\Nminta bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi mendengarkan apa, Kamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku tahu lagu ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Gujyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu hebat banget\Nkarena rela lembur, Kamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada tugas, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku agak kesulitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:15:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gujyo Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mahasiswi S2 tahun pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penghuni asrama yang lebih tua\Ndariku dan Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin dia sangat cerdas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru kali ini aku mengobrol dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hapus baris 35 hingga 40,\Nlalu coba jalankan sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggal sedikit lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah membantuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadwalmu masih padat dan berat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu jurusan apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manajemen Teknik.\NFakultas Sains dan Teknologi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, sama seperti Ibuki, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lebih sibuk dari aku dan Ibuki,\Ntapi apa waktu mainmu aman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belanja bareng teman-teman sekelas,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mampir ke acara penyambutan\Nanggota sirkel,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan minum-minum bareng Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya Ibuki selalu minum sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku heran saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin kamu dianggap spesial.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata Kak Gujyo merokok, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf! Aku merokok tanpa sadar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kumatikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau wanita cantik sepertimu merokok,\Nkamu terlihat seperti artis terkenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru kali ini ada yang bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sangat lucu, ya, Kamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mirip artis, katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kalau tugasmu sudah selesai,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mau menghabiskan waktu denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu nonton film apa belakangan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toy Story, mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah masuk ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau yang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kayaknya rumit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tontonan orang dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak yakin bisa menikmatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Kak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak botol minuman keras\Nyang indah di rak ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya seperti permata saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh kuminum?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua itu punya Ibuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.\NIni minuman favoritku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini miras?\NAtau air biasa? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sepertinya ada rasa buahnya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya ringan dan tidak membekas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru kali ini aku meminumnya,\Ntapi rasanya sangat enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa seenak itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu Ibuki suka minuman keras ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua Asrama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dikasih minum lagi,\Nmungkin aku akan tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uenak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uenak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Segelas lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah cukup! Berhenti!\NNanti habis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana menurutmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan cuma "eh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa menurutmu Ibuki\Nmau minum itu bersamaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya Ketua Asrama\Npilih-pilih soal minuman keras?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir sake ini enak dan dia pasti suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Minum bersamaku"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo, apa kita tadi bahas itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Gujyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ekspresi wajahmu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyadari sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan, kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu menyukai Ketua Asrama, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu imut banget, Kak Gujyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha-Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa maksudmu?\NKamu salah paham!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku hanya merasa kalau Ibuki\N- Tapi, karena masalah cegukan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- sering memilih sake\N- Tapi, karena masalah cegukan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- di antara minuman lain saat minum sendirian.\N- dia tidak suka minum dengan orang lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- di antara minuman lain saat minum sendirian.\N- kecuali aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahu, kan?\NDia sudah jadi Ketua Asrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin merayakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata sake ini enak banget, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah menyembunyikan rasa malu\Nseperti anak kecil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu enggak imut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo habiskan saja, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita berdua sama, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tadi bukan kepingin minum,\Ntapi kepingin kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pengin lidahmu.
